{"Code":"021383","Name":"Monachus Park ","Description":"This modern hotel is located just some 3 minutes on foot from the long sandy beach. Restaurants, bars, nightclubs and shops lie around 500 m away. The tourist centre is about 8 km from the hotel, and the town centre roughly 10 km. The hotel has good public transport links (bus) and a public transport stop is only steps away. Antalya airport is located approximately 65 km away.\n\nThis air-conditioned beach hotel is surrounded by extensive gardens and terraces and comprises a total of 265 rooms spread over 4 floors. The inviting lobby offers guests a 24-hour reception desk, a hotel safe, a cloakroom, and a currency exchange desk. There are also lifts, a caf\u00E9, a newspaper stand, a small supermarket, various shops, a hairdressing salon, a bar, a nightclub, an auditorium, and a games room. Dining options include an air-conditioned \u00E0 la carte restaurant with a non-smoking area and highchairs available for children, while there is a conference room for business guests and WLAN is on offer for an additional fee. A laundry service, medical assistance and bike hire round up the offerings. Younger guests may let off steam in the playground as well as participate in kids\u0027 club activities. A car park is available for those arriving by car.\n\nEach of the stylish rooms, suites and apartments comes with an en suite bathroom and a hairdryer, a direct dial telephone, satellite/ cable TV and a radio. Guests will also find a double bed and individually-controlled air conditioning and heating in the attractive rooms, as well as a balcony or terrace, a minibar, and a hire safe. The apartments feature a combined bedroom/ lounge area and a separate bedroom.","Category":"5 STARS","Chain":"","AccommodationType":"Hotel","Destination":"Antalya","District":"Side","Address":{"Street":"P.K.15 \u00C7olakli Manavgat","PostCode":"07620","City":"SIDE","CountryCode":"TR"},"Facilities":[{"Name":"Total number of rooms","IsFree":tru